        {
          "id": "88e2d5e8-9f8d-9fde-9920-063f377a4830",
          "title": "Gallery: Series One",
          "slug": "gallery-series-one",
          "order": 2,
          "parent": null,
          "indent": 0,
          "content": "<h2>Series One</h2><media-image source=\"https://www.galleryone.com/Merchant5/graphics/00000001/packard-pacan1_500x401.jpg\" card citation=\"Freedim\" accent-color=\"grey\" size=\"wide\"></media-image><h3>Be Stillness</h3><p>Freedim is a representation of stillness. The ocean mirrors life’s quiet truth: I am not merely a drop in the sea, but the sea within a single drop.</p>",
          "metadata": {
            "published": "1",
