          "order": 3,
          "parent": null,
          "indent": 0,
          "content": "<h2>Series Two</h2><p>This work explores the world through a child’s eyes—first contact with color, imagination, and presence.</p><media-image source=\"https://d7hftxdivxxvm.cloudfront.net/?quality=80&resize_to=width&src=https%3A%2F%2Fd32dm0rphc51dk.cloudfront.net%2F4H7Xsg7mSdX7nn55b31JnQ%2Fnormalized.jpg&width=910\" card citation=\"Kolor\" accent-color=\"grey\" size=\"wide\"></media-image>",
